EmailTemplate.subject: C:IO Labs Live Stream Starts in 2 Hours
EmailTemplate.textOnly: We Can't Wait To See You At Turbofest Silicon Valley The AWS Loft | March 9, 2016 <[[http://vmturbo.com/turbofest-silicon-valley]]> {{Lead.First Name:default=}} The inaugural C:IO Labs live streaming Q&A session starts in 2 hours! We’ll focus on private cloud—touching on hybrid, public, and multi-cloud—but the conversation is what you make it. We will take your questions online during the event—just use the YouTube chat window on the right. Who: Charles Crouchman, VMTurbo CTO What: Private Cloud ~ Live Steaming Q&A When: March 23, 2016 at 1:00pm EST Where: C:IO Labs YouTube Livestream <[[https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=tOxjuoVCRbo]]> - The VMTurbo Team
